            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">巨竹電子表單簽核系統</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul class="flex space-x-4">
                    <li><a href="#introduction" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">專案簡介</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#features" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">系統設計</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#challenges" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">挑戰與方案</a></li>
